<title> Character Abilities <>
<content>
    <section> Overview <>
        <p>As characters develop, they will acquire two main sets of abilities, feats and spells.<>
        <p> Feats will provide boosts or modifiers to different actions the character can take.<>
        <p> Spells are actions the character can take by using mana to manifest some sort of effect.<>
